data.description: Fall in love this spacious two-story, 5 bedroom, 3 bathroom home on almost a quarter acre (.23) situated on a cul-de-sac! Newly painted both Exterior and Interior areas of the home! Recently installed ceiling fans in every bedroom. As you drive up, you can not help but to notice the paver driveway leading up to the two-car garage and newly sealed stone accents near the front door entrance. Plenty of space to spread out with 2,426 sq ft of living area. Whip up your favorite meals in the eat-in kitchen complete with stainless steel appliances, natural granite countertops, modern backsplash, recessed lighting and breakfast bar accented with decorative corbels. Sit down to your wonderful meal in the formal dining room or keep it casual at the dinette area. Entertain your guests in the living room that features a stylish accented wall section with built-in electric fireplace. A bedroom is conveniently located on the first floor and full bathroom. Heading upstairs you will land at the loft with a built-in desk. Retreat to the master suite with an ensuite bathroom featuring dual sinks, granite counter tops, walk-in closet, shower and a separate garden tub to soak away the stress from the day. There are three other ample sized bedrooms on the second floor to suit all of your needs. The laundry room is conveniently located upstairs as well. Time to head outside to the oversized backyard. Lounge on the spacious screened enclosed patio overlooking the viny fenced backyard. The vinyl fencing gives you that extra privacy you desire. Take advantage of the area with room for gardening, playing and entertainment. Let's not forget about the citrus and vegetable trees to take advantage of! Conveniently located in gated community of Eustis Spring Ridge Estates which is minutes away from breathtaking scenic lake views, blueberry pick farms, lake water sports, boat tours and even seaplane rides! And downtown Mount Dora giving you plenty of shopping, dining and entertainment. Don't miss out on this beautiful home!
